host_about:
I live in Asheville with my 3 children, 2 cats and dog. Moved from Florida in 2000. 
I love all the stories I hear that go something like "My truck broke down when I was driving through Asheville. That was 8 years ago and I'm still here."   This truly is a special place. These mountains just feel like home to so many people no matter how far they've traveled. 
I've thought for ages that I would love to have a vacation rental, to create a little spot of my design that people would visit and enjoy. Thanks to Airbnb and life's little twists and turns, I now get to have that experience :~}

